name: "Cat Drone Harness" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing made on my phone.] I was in a fun Twitter Space a few days ago in which the group was given prompts and then asked to quickly draw the prompt. I only got to play one round before I had family invade the house, but I thought the sketch was pretty funny. Here, for those who might agree, is a super-cheap, quick sketch from a nonsense prompt!
